The '''Ado Spine''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace trade route]] in the [[Ado sector/Legends|Ado sector]] in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]].<ref name="TEA" /> The Spine passed connected all the major [[Planet/Legends|planets]] and [[Star system/Legends|systems]] that were located in the [[Sector/Legends|sector]], such as the [[Induparan Crown Worlds]]. The [[Shadowport/Legends|shadowport]], [[StarForge Station]], located in the nearby [[StarForge Nebula/Legends|StarForge Nebula]], was a popular stop along the route for [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] and [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] such [[Urias Xhaxin]].

